WEBVTT

00:01:34.640 --> 00:01:37.039
I hope our preparations are sufficient.

00:01:40.120 --> 00:01:41.320
We should trust them.

00:02:55.280 --> 00:02:55.960
Report.

00:02:57.360 --> 00:02:58.880
The Yutu-2 lunar rover

00:02:59.040 --> 00:03:00.960
has reached the designated location.

00:03:00.960 --> 00:03:03.600
Taking photos of each other with the Haoyue-4 probe

00:03:03.600 --> 00:03:04.720
was successful.

00:03:11.520 --> 00:03:13.180
Images have been downloaded.

00:03:14.280 --> 00:03:16.140
Ground processing shows normal.

00:03:16.840 --> 00:03:19.120
The mutual photographing of the two devices

00:03:19.120 --> 00:03:19.850
is complete.

00:03:28.040 --> 00:03:29.500
The mutual photographing

00:03:29.840 --> 00:03:31.170
was a complete success.

00:03:31.240 --> 00:03:31.920
Copy that.

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:33.079
Good.

00:03:57.120 --> 00:03:57.920
We succeeded.

00:04:00.280 --> 00:04:01.200
Great.

00:04:13.920 --> 00:04:14.600
Comrades.

00:04:15.000 --> 00:04:16.360
According to

00:04:16.360 --> 00:04:18.519
the Aerospace Flight Control Center,

00:04:19.160 --> 00:04:20.760
the Haoyue-4 probe

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:24.320
in the Von Kármán crater

00:04:25.080 --> 00:04:27.410
has achieved an autonomous soft landing.

00:04:27.800 --> 00:04:29.360
Mutual photographing of the two devices

00:04:29.360 --> 00:04:30.220
is successful.

00:04:31.640 --> 00:04:33.840
The first photo of the far side of the moon in human history

00:04:33.840 --> 00:04:36.000
was taken in 1959,

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:39.280
exactly sixty years ago.

00:04:39.800 --> 00:04:41.320
In these short 60 years,

00:04:41.800 --> 00:04:43.600
China's aerospace engineering

00:04:43.800 --> 00:04:46.600
has completed the leap from nothing to something,

00:04:46.920 --> 00:04:50.040
and from lagging behind to leading.

00:04:51.240 --> 00:04:54.200
It also marks that our country's aerospace engineering

00:04:54.200 --> 00:04:58.720
has filled the gap in the history of human landing exploration.

00:04:59.040 --> 00:05:00.560
Now I announce,

00:05:00.560 --> 00:05:02.400
The landing of the Haoyue-4

00:05:03.360 --> 00:05:04.760
mission probe

00:05:05.200 --> 00:05:06.880
was a complete success.

00:05:08.200 --> 00:05:08.920
Here,

00:05:09.640 --> 00:05:12.800
I would like to extend my warm congratulations to the units

00:05:12.800 --> 00:05:16.600
and all the researchers and testers participating in this mission.

00:05:16.920 --> 00:05:17.880
I would like to

00:05:17.880 --> 00:05:19.920
express my warmest congratulations.

00:05:19.920 --> 00:05:20.960
And to

00:05:20.960 --> 00:05:23.760
the leaders and experts who came to guide us,

00:05:24.240 --> 00:05:26.170
I express my heartfelt gratitude.

00:05:43.880 --> 00:05:45.360
Run, rabbit.

00:05:51.360 --> 00:05:52.420
What are you doing?

00:05:57.280 --> 00:05:58.840
I'm sending a message to our childhood selves,

00:05:58.840 --> 00:05:59.720
to tell them

00:05:59.920 --> 00:06:00.600
no matter what,

00:06:00.600 --> 00:06:01.760
never give up.

00:06:10.800 --> 00:06:12.360
Do you believe in aliens?

00:06:15.280 --> 00:06:16.120
I do.

00:06:35.159 --> 00:06:37.159
What do you want to say to the aliens?

00:06:37.640 --> 00:06:39.200
I want to make a wish to them.

00:06:39.960 --> 00:06:41.420
Then I want to make one too.

00:07:04.560 --> 00:07:06.200
As for the current work of Haoyue-4,

00:07:06.200 --> 00:07:08.060
it has been basically completed.

00:07:08.080 --> 00:07:09.800
Here, on behalf of the center,

00:07:09.800 --> 00:07:11.040
I would like to thank you all.

00:07:11.040 --> 00:07:12.880
You are all excellent.

00:07:14.080 --> 00:07:17.520
This time, our flight control team in the Xingqiao relay satellite

00:07:17.520 --> 00:07:19.040
and Haoyue-4 missions

00:07:19.280 --> 00:07:21.080
performed exceptionally well.

00:07:21.160 --> 00:07:22.720
The leadership has decided that,

00:07:22.720 --> 00:07:23.880
Comrade Chu Jiajia

00:07:24.200 --> 00:07:25.720
meets the seniority requirements.

00:07:25.720 --> 00:07:27.960
Her professional title is promoted from Senior Engineer

00:07:27.960 --> 00:07:29.320
to Researcher.

00:07:29.320 --> 00:07:30.980
Round of applause, everyone.

00:07:33.880 --> 00:07:35.040
China Aerospace.

00:07:36.920 --> 00:07:38.920
Thank you, Mr. Qin and Mr. Gu.

00:07:39.159 --> 00:07:40.690
I will keep up the good work.

00:07:40.720 --> 00:07:41.440
Have a seat.

00:07:44.920 --> 00:07:47.280
I wish Wei and Qi were here.

00:07:48.200 --> 00:07:48.880
Alright.

00:07:49.400 --> 00:07:51.800
They would be even sadder if they were here.

00:07:52.760 --> 00:07:53.600
Next,

00:07:54.600 --> 00:07:56.280
we will face

00:07:56.280 --> 00:07:57.640
the more complex

00:07:58.240 --> 00:08:00.160
and technologically demanding

00:08:00.160 --> 00:08:01.240
Haoyue 5 mission.

00:08:01.480 --> 00:08:03.140
There will be more challenges

00:08:03.320 --> 00:08:04.720
and newer difficulties.

00:08:04.960 --> 00:08:06.160
Are you confident we can complete it?

00:08:06.160 --> 00:08:07.400
Yes.

00:08:08.720 --> 00:08:09.360
Okay.

00:08:09.600 --> 00:08:10.880
Next, I will assign

00:08:10.880 --> 00:08:12.160
the following tasks.

00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:14.130
Comrade Chu Jiajia,

00:08:14.360 --> 00:08:16.160
will be in charge of the Haoyue-5

00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:18.170
Earth-Moon orbit flight control.

00:08:18.320 --> 00:08:19.840
Everyone must fully cooperate.

00:08:19.840 --> 00:08:21.760
The drilling and sampling of lunar soil,

00:08:21.760 --> 00:08:23.040
and the rendezvous and docking of the ascender,

00:08:23.040 --> 00:08:24.360
orbiter, and returner

00:08:24.360 --> 00:08:25.690
will be handled by Xu Xu.

00:08:26.720 --> 00:08:27.840
You need to be prepared

00:08:27.840 --> 00:08:28.880
to go to Xi'an at any time.

00:08:28.880 --> 00:08:29.560
Yes.

00:08:30.080 --> 00:08:30.760
Now,

00:08:30.760 --> 00:08:32.419
I want to emphasize one thing.

00:08:32.799 --> 00:08:34.799
The center's leadership has decided

00:08:34.799 --> 00:08:37.159
that comrades Qu Ruonan and Cai Bo'ao

00:08:37.360 --> 00:08:39.240
will assist in designing

00:08:39.240 --> 00:08:41.600
the flight control plan for atmospheric re-entry

00:08:41.600 --> 00:08:44.520
and landing during the return mission.

00:08:45.000 --> 00:08:45.960
I hope you

00:08:46.280 --> 00:08:48.480
won't let down the flight control team's expectations.

00:08:48.480 --> 00:08:49.210
Understood.

00:08:53.520 --> 00:08:54.280
Have a seat.

00:09:05.840 --> 00:09:06.640
That's all.

00:09:15.360 --> 00:09:15.960
Come in.

00:09:17.840 --> 00:09:18.720
Seniors,

00:09:18.960 --> 00:09:20.160
we're here to report.

00:09:20.480 --> 00:09:22.160
I've heard about what happened recently.

00:09:22.160 --> 00:09:23.040
But since you are here

00:09:23.040 --> 00:09:24.280
in our Daily Monitoring Group,

00:09:24.280 --> 00:09:25.360
I hope you can adapt

00:09:25.360 --> 00:09:27.160
to the work pace and requirements here.

00:09:27.160 --> 00:09:28.440
Stick to your posts

00:09:28.440 --> 00:09:29.320
and work hard.

00:09:29.320 --> 00:09:30.760
Our Daily Monitoring Group

00:09:30.760 --> 00:09:32.960
is mainly responsible for the daily monitoring of satellites in orbit.

00:09:32.960 --> 00:09:34.690
The work intensity is not high,

00:09:35.040 --> 00:09:37.520
mainly duty and monitoring work,

00:09:37.520 --> 00:09:39.120
but it's all very important.

00:09:40.000 --> 00:09:40.730
Understood.

00:09:40.800 --> 00:09:42.200
Please assign us work.

00:09:42.440 --> 00:09:43.840
We just got a new task.

00:09:43.840 --> 00:09:45.600
Currently, the Lifeng-1 weather satellite

00:09:45.600 --> 00:09:47.360
is affected by space debris in orbit.

00:09:47.360 --> 00:09:48.920
It requires real-time monitoring,

00:09:48.920 --> 00:09:50.200
so I'll leave it in your hands.

00:09:50.200 --> 00:09:51.800
Here are your workstations.

00:10:27.200 --> 00:10:29.260
Are you getting used to the transfer?

00:10:30.920 --> 00:10:34.160
Routine monitoring is an extension of the launch mission.

00:10:34.160 --> 00:10:35.640
It's also an important position

00:10:35.640 --> 00:10:37.500
where you can make achievements.

00:10:38.720 --> 00:10:40.780
I've thought it through, Sister Jia.

00:10:41.040 --> 00:10:41.920
This time,

00:10:42.240 --> 00:10:43.240
it was my fault.

00:10:43.920 --> 00:10:45.180
It won't happen again.

00:10:47.320 --> 00:10:48.320
If you take a fall,

00:10:48.320 --> 00:10:49.600
you have to get back up yourself.

00:10:49.600 --> 00:10:51.730
Then the fall wasn't in vain, you know?

00:10:55.560 --> 00:10:56.240
Sister Jia,

00:10:56.920 --> 00:10:58.780
I'll transfer the airfare to you.

00:10:59.160 --> 00:11:00.360
That's enough.

00:11:00.640 --> 00:11:01.520
No need.

00:11:04.160 --> 00:11:04.920
It's over.

00:11:04.920 --> 00:11:07.320
Worrying less about you would be better than anything.

00:11:07.320 --> 00:11:08.600
You keep me on edge all day long.

00:11:08.600 --> 00:11:09.400
There's no end to it.

00:11:09.400 --> 00:11:11.600
When will you ever give me peace of mind?

00:11:12.400 --> 00:11:14.360
Making Jia worried

00:11:14.920 --> 00:11:16.000
is my honor.

00:11:16.760 --> 00:11:18.160
Alright, go on now.

00:11:18.160 --> 00:11:18.880
Go to work.

00:11:23.400 --> 00:11:24.120
Jia.

00:11:24.520 --> 00:11:25.480
I'll say it again.

00:11:25.480 --> 00:11:26.560
No matter what happens in the future,

00:11:26.560 --> 00:11:28.280
whether I work for you or not,

00:11:29.160 --> 00:11:30.290
I am grateful to you.

00:12:07.400 --> 00:12:08.800
Tonight's satellite orbit change

00:12:08.800 --> 00:12:10.530
Wu Wei and Ying Ziqi are on duty.

00:12:10.640 --> 00:12:11.720
I'll be with them.

00:12:11.720 --> 00:12:13.580
You should go back and rest early.

00:12:13.600 --> 00:12:14.660
Oh, one more thing.

00:12:14.920 --> 00:12:16.080
The center asked us last time

00:12:16.080 --> 00:12:18.120
to select people for the deep space array mission.

00:12:18.120 --> 00:12:20.040
We don't have suitable candidates here.

00:12:20.040 --> 00:12:22.040
I'll write a reply to turn them down.

00:12:22.640 --> 00:12:24.240
We are indeed short-handed.

00:12:24.360 --> 00:12:25.280
Let's do that.

00:12:28.320 --> 00:12:29.000
Wu Wei.

00:12:29.160 --> 00:12:30.520
Run an errand for me later.

00:12:30.520 --> 00:12:32.720
Deliver a document to Mr. Zhang Ziming.

00:12:33.480 --> 00:12:34.040
Okay.

00:12:54.640 --> 00:12:55.320
Mr. Zhang,

00:12:55.920 --> 00:12:58.520
here are the daily monitoring team documents.

00:13:01.600 --> 00:13:02.400
Mr. Zhang,

00:13:02.720 --> 00:13:04.320
when will our deep space array mission

00:13:04.320 --> 00:13:05.320
start?

00:13:05.640 --> 00:13:06.680
Why do you ask?

00:13:06.680 --> 00:13:08.280
It has nothing to do with you.

00:13:08.800 --> 00:13:09.680
I heard the whole center

00:13:09.680 --> 00:13:11.400
received instructions for selection.

00:13:11.400 --> 00:13:13.200
Can everyone apply?

00:13:13.200 --> 00:13:15.160
That's right. Everyone can apply,

00:13:16.600 --> 00:13:17.520
except you.

00:13:20.760 --> 00:13:22.280
Because even if you apply,

00:13:22.280 --> 00:13:23.240
I won't pick you.

00:13:23.640 --> 00:13:25.640
You are not qualified enough for me.

00:13:40.280 --> 00:13:40.880
Thank you.

00:13:44.120 --> 00:13:45.180
How is Wu Wei doing?

00:13:45.440 --> 00:13:46.360
I heard

00:13:46.360 --> 00:13:47.680
you went to Jiuquan.

00:13:47.800 --> 00:13:49.130
Is everything alright?

00:13:55.800 --> 00:13:56.800
Here's the thing.

00:13:57.880 --> 00:13:58.840
The higher-ups

00:13:58.840 --> 00:14:00.160
decided to put me in charge

00:14:00.160 --> 00:14:01.720
of the lunar soil drilling and sampling,

00:14:01.720 --> 00:14:03.760
and the ascender, orbiter,

00:14:03.760 --> 00:14:06.560
and returner's rendezvous and docking missions.

00:14:08.320 --> 00:14:09.920
I'll be leaving in a few days.

00:14:10.400 --> 00:14:11.160
To Xi'an.

00:14:13.160 --> 00:14:14.220
Congratulations.

00:14:15.280 --> 00:14:16.880
Don't just congratulate me.

00:14:17.520 --> 00:14:18.850
Tell me about yourself.

00:14:22.000 --> 00:14:23.200
With your abilities,

00:14:23.800 --> 00:14:25.120
do you really plan

00:14:25.120 --> 00:14:27.250
to stay in the daily monitoring group?

00:14:31.120 --> 00:14:32.040
It's fine.

00:14:32.920 --> 00:14:34.680
Since the leaders arranged for me to be here,

00:14:34.680 --> 00:14:35.610
I will do my best.

00:14:36.200 --> 00:14:39.330
The work of the monitoring group is also very important.

00:14:41.000 --> 00:14:44.060
Of course I know the importance of the monitoring team.

00:14:46.240 --> 00:14:48.170
Don't you want to do core missions?

00:14:52.720 --> 00:14:53.520
I believe

00:14:54.080 --> 00:14:54.960
you came to Flight Control

00:14:54.960 --> 00:14:56.480
not just for this.

00:14:58.600 --> 00:15:00.060
What are you trying to say?

00:15:01.080 --> 00:15:02.440
I'll tell you straight.

00:15:03.600 --> 00:15:04.680
In Aerospace City,

00:15:05.040 --> 00:15:06.280
there is no precedent of being transferred out

00:15:06.280 --> 00:15:07.810
and then transferred back.

00:15:10.720 --> 00:15:12.250
Having worked on Haoyue-4,

00:15:13.040 --> 00:15:15.170
are you willing to just stay like this?

00:15:25.280 --> 00:15:26.680
This mission is a brand-new challenge

00:15:26.680 --> 00:15:28.680
for me

00:15:28.680 --> 00:15:30.360
and for everyone.

00:15:30.600 --> 00:15:31.880
To break through the impossible

00:15:31.880 --> 00:15:33.080
and make it possible,

00:15:33.840 --> 00:15:34.920
I need hands

00:15:35.160 --> 00:15:36.240
and a partner.

00:15:36.680 --> 00:15:38.340
The superiors gave me a quota,

00:15:38.720 --> 00:15:40.360
and I get to decide the candidate.

00:15:40.360 --> 00:15:42.020
I think you are very suitable.

00:15:43.280 --> 00:15:43.960
So are you willing

00:15:43.960 --> 00:15:45.160
to go to Xi'an with me?

00:15:48.960 --> 00:15:50.120
You mean

00:15:51.760 --> 00:15:53.490
I can go back to Flight Control?

00:15:53.720 --> 00:15:54.320
Yes.

00:15:54.640 --> 00:15:55.640
What about Wu Wei?

00:15:56.080 --> 00:15:57.120
Can both of us go?

00:15:57.560 --> 00:15:58.400
No.

00:15:59.040 --> 00:16:00.300
There is only one spot.

00:16:00.680 --> 00:16:01.940
Between the two of you,

00:16:02.160 --> 00:16:03.040
I chose you.

00:16:15.560 --> 00:16:17.490
I know you're worried about Wu Wei.

00:16:17.880 --> 00:16:19.340
You two are good partners.

00:16:19.560 --> 00:16:20.760
To cheer him up,

00:16:20.960 --> 00:16:22.960
you went to the Gobi Desert thousands of kilometers away

00:16:22.960 --> 00:16:24.920
to keep him company and clear his mind.

00:16:24.920 --> 00:16:26.650
But Ziqi, you need to know this.

00:16:27.080 --> 00:16:29.240
Your dream is in your own hands.

00:16:30.360 --> 00:16:31.160
Besides, Wu Wei

00:16:31.160 --> 00:16:32.600
has his own path to walk.

00:16:33.840 --> 00:16:34.840
I hope this time,

00:16:34.840 --> 00:16:36.370
you can think for yourself.

00:16:47.920 --> 00:16:48.920
Give me some time.

00:16:49.040 --> 00:16:50.640
It's not that I won't give you time,

00:16:50.640 --> 00:16:53.700
but the higher-ups are anxious for the mission roster.

00:16:59.200 --> 00:17:00.120
How about this?

00:17:02.320 --> 00:17:04.520
I'll give you tonight to think about it.

00:17:05.359 --> 00:17:06.890
Give me an answer tomorrow.

00:17:09.720 --> 00:17:10.359
Okay.

00:17:26.000 --> 00:17:28.280
Right, anyone can sign up,

00:17:28.480 --> 00:17:29.480
except you.

00:17:32.320 --> 00:17:34.320
You are not qualified enough for me.

00:17:34.320 --> 00:17:35.000
Got it?

00:17:44.800 --> 00:17:46.330
Having worked on Haoyue-4,

00:17:47.080 --> 00:17:48.940
are you content to just stay here?

00:17:49.480 --> 00:17:51.680
Don't you want to work on core missions?

00:17:53.600 --> 00:17:54.660
In Aerospace City,

00:17:55.040 --> 00:17:56.360
there's no precedent of being transferred out

00:17:56.360 --> 00:17:57.960
and then transferring back.

00:17:59.840 --> 00:18:01.960
Dreams are in your own hands.

00:18:04.400 --> 00:18:05.600
And Wu Wei also has his own path

00:18:05.600 --> 00:18:06.480
to choose.

00:18:06.680 --> 00:18:07.440
I hope

00:18:07.840 --> 00:18:09.900
you can think for yourself this time.

00:18:15.880 --> 00:18:16.360
Come.

00:18:16.360 --> 00:18:18.620
I have something to discuss with you all.

00:18:23.720 --> 00:18:25.450
The center has assigned a task.

00:18:25.760 --> 00:18:27.560
We have an exchange activity

00:18:27.560 --> 00:18:29.040
with the World Aerospace Association.

00:18:29.040 --> 00:18:29.880
The center hopes

00:18:29.880 --> 00:18:31.440
we can send someone over

00:18:31.440 --> 00:18:32.370
for an exchange.

00:18:33.640 --> 00:18:34.720
How long will it be?

00:18:34.960 --> 00:18:35.600
One year.

00:18:37.200 --> 00:18:38.160
You veterans

00:18:38.360 --> 00:18:39.600
discuss it, okay?

00:18:41.800 --> 00:18:42.720
You will be in charge of this.

00:18:42.720 --> 00:18:44.360
Give me a candidate later.

00:18:51.440 --> 00:18:52.280
Go to work.

00:18:53.400 --> 00:18:54.280
Senior You,

00:18:54.560 --> 00:18:55.200
tell me.

00:18:55.200 --> 00:18:57.520
Going abroad for exchange is a good thing.

00:18:57.520 --> 00:18:59.650
Why does it feel like no one wants to go?

00:19:00.360 --> 00:19:01.490
Are you stupid, kid?

00:19:02.320 --> 00:19:02.840
Think about it.

00:19:02.840 --> 00:19:05.360
We just announced entering the Haoyue-5 mission,

00:19:05.360 --> 00:19:06.400
and then this comes up.

00:19:06.400 --> 00:19:08.240
Being transferred abroad for exchange

00:19:08.240 --> 00:19:09.280
is equivalent to being removed from the mission, isn't it?

00:19:09.280 --> 00:19:10.200
All right, stop talking.

00:19:10.200 --> 00:19:10.860
Get to work.

00:19:12.440 --> 00:19:13.040
Okay.

00:19:26.520 --> 00:19:27.120
Hello.

00:19:27.360 --> 00:19:28.200
Hello, Ziqi.

00:19:28.800 --> 00:19:30.260
Have you made up your mind?

00:19:30.640 --> 00:19:31.520
The mission roster,

00:19:31.520 --> 00:19:32.850
I need to submit it ASAP.

00:19:37.520 --> 00:19:38.450
I'll go with you.

00:19:42.080 --> 00:19:43.880
You won't regret this decision.

00:19:49.160 --> 00:19:50.200
Give me some time.

00:19:50.920 --> 00:19:51.720
No problem.

00:19:51.720 --> 00:19:53.180
I'll wait to hear from you.

00:19:53.840 --> 00:19:54.440
Okay.

00:19:58.520 --> 00:19:59.200
Go quickly.

00:19:59.200 --> 00:19:59.760
Okay.

00:20:02.600 --> 00:20:03.280
By the way, this satellite...

00:20:03.280 --> 00:20:03.920
Senior Sister.

00:20:03.920 --> 00:20:04.780
Where is Wu Wei?

00:20:05.160 --> 00:20:07.960
I think he went to the archives to do some research.

00:20:09.080 --> 00:20:10.920
It has already changed its orbit.

00:20:10.920 --> 00:20:12.720
I'll keep a close eye on it later.

00:20:35.080 --> 00:20:35.810
You're back.

00:20:36.800 --> 00:20:37.930
You're still awake?

00:20:38.640 --> 00:20:39.720
I was waiting for you for dinner.

00:20:39.720 --> 00:20:40.780
Why are you so late?

00:20:41.080 --> 00:20:42.120
I was busy with something.

00:20:42.120 --> 00:20:44.580
Don't wait for me next time. Eat by yourself.

00:20:45.520 --> 00:20:46.850
What were you busy with?

00:20:55.040 --> 00:20:56.240
Do you know Zhang Ziming was transferred to take charge of

00:20:56.240 --> 00:20:57.900
the deep space array mission?

00:20:59.040 --> 00:20:59.840
You want to go?

00:21:02.120 --> 00:21:03.050
He didn't agree.

00:21:08.120 --> 00:21:08.720
Sit.

00:21:15.640 --> 00:21:16.400
I know.

00:21:16.400 --> 00:21:18.860
We agreed to do our best in daily monitoring.

00:21:20.840 --> 00:21:21.600
But,

00:21:22.600 --> 00:21:23.660
I want to try again.

00:21:24.440 --> 00:21:25.700
I want to go to Kashgar.

00:21:26.360 --> 00:21:28.120
Actually,

00:21:28.120 --> 00:21:29.920
I have something to tell you too.

00:21:33.000 --> 00:21:34.360
Xu Xu came to see me.

00:21:37.040 --> 00:21:39.520
He wants me to help him complete the Hao-5 mission.

00:21:39.520 --> 00:21:40.850
To retrieve lunar soil.

00:21:42.480 --> 00:21:44.140
I'll be transferred to Xi'an,

00:21:44.200 --> 00:21:45.080
to complete the rendezvous and docking

00:21:45.080 --> 00:21:47.600
of the ascender and the orbiter-returner combination.

00:21:47.600 --> 00:21:48.560
Did you agree?

00:21:50.160 --> 00:21:51.960
I thought about it for a long time

00:21:52.320 --> 00:21:53.320
and decided to go.

00:21:54.760 --> 00:21:56.680
That's a good thing.

00:21:58.720 --> 00:22:00.720
Not everyone gets to dig lunar soil.

00:22:06.000 --> 00:22:06.800
In that case,

00:22:07.000 --> 00:22:09.260
I'm not the one standing you up this time.

00:22:11.960 --> 00:22:13.320
That paper you've been writing recently,

00:22:13.320 --> 00:22:14.840
is for the deep space array, right?

00:22:14.840 --> 00:22:16.800
How far along are you? Let me take a look.

00:22:16.800 --> 00:22:17.680
No need, bro.

00:22:18.560 --> 00:22:19.880
This time,

00:22:19.880 --> 00:22:21.080
I want to do it myself.

00:22:25.240 --> 00:22:26.370
When you go to Xi'an,

00:22:27.160 --> 00:22:28.290
don't embarrass me.

00:22:28.840 --> 00:22:29.840
See you at the top.

00:22:31.040 --> 00:22:32.040
See you at the top.

00:22:42.080 --> 00:22:43.400
Morning, everyone.

00:22:43.400 --> 00:22:43.960
Morning.

00:22:43.960 --> 00:22:45.080
Alright, stop what you're doing.

00:22:45.080 --> 00:22:46.240
It's my treat today.

00:22:46.600 --> 00:22:48.480
Plenty of snacks and milk tea for everyone.

00:22:48.480 --> 00:22:49.640
I was just craving milk tea.

00:22:49.640 --> 00:22:52.000
Mr. Jiang, do you have some good news today?

00:22:52.000 --> 00:22:53.600
Share it with us.

00:22:54.360 --> 00:22:55.200
There's more over here.

00:22:55.200 --> 00:22:56.400
What's the good news?

00:22:57.560 --> 00:22:58.520
Tell us.

00:22:59.080 --> 00:23:00.880
Since everyone is here,

00:23:00.880 --> 00:23:02.160
I'll make an announcement.

00:23:02.160 --> 00:23:03.240
I have decided

00:23:03.240 --> 00:23:05.570
to take on the overseas exchange mission.

00:23:07.040 --> 00:23:07.800
What?

00:23:08.280 --> 00:23:09.280
Here's the thing.

00:23:09.880 --> 00:23:10.960
We have a mission right now,

00:23:10.960 --> 00:23:12.560
and there are only a few of us.

00:23:13.040 --> 00:23:14.720
Yanyan's child is still young.

00:23:14.720 --> 00:23:16.360
Youxiu is in the rising stage of her career.

00:23:16.360 --> 00:23:18.120
And Jiajia is

00:23:18.120 --> 00:23:18.960
the person in charge of the Haoyue Project.

00:23:18.960 --> 00:23:21.160
So it's not suitable for any of you to go.

00:23:22.800 --> 00:23:23.520
But

00:23:24.080 --> 00:23:26.200
this is a task assigned by our superiors after all,

00:23:26.200 --> 00:23:28.000
and we must actively cooperate.

00:23:33.200 --> 00:23:35.240
During the time working with you all,

00:23:35.240 --> 00:23:36.400
I was very happy.

00:23:36.720 --> 00:23:38.000
Although I won't be on the mission anymore,

00:23:38.000 --> 00:23:38.920
I am still

00:23:38.920 --> 00:23:40.640
a member of our team.

00:23:40.640 --> 00:23:41.960
That won't change.

00:23:42.560 --> 00:23:44.840
Can we talk to Lao Gu about this?

00:23:45.800 --> 00:23:46.480
We don't necessarily have to

00:23:46.480 --> 00:23:48.080
send someone from here, right?

00:23:48.080 --> 00:23:48.680
Right?

00:23:48.920 --> 00:23:50.680
It's just an exchange, a routine task.

00:23:50.680 --> 00:23:51.920
Anyone can go.

00:23:51.920 --> 00:23:53.200
You can't leave.

00:23:53.200 --> 00:23:54.480
You are our main force.

00:23:55.280 --> 00:23:56.120
Yeah, Mengyao.

00:23:56.120 --> 00:23:57.980
Please think about it carefully.

00:23:58.000 --> 00:23:58.720
Alright.

00:23:59.520 --> 00:24:01.600
Actually, Lao Gu is also in a difficult position.

00:24:01.600 --> 00:24:03.480
In recent years, our aerospace industry

00:24:03.480 --> 00:24:05.040
has been booming.

00:24:05.040 --> 00:24:06.320
But for various reasons,

00:24:06.320 --> 00:24:08.680
we have been lacking international communication.

00:24:08.680 --> 00:24:09.880
Some people want to set up a blockade,

00:24:09.880 --> 00:24:10.920
but we don't.

00:24:11.280 --> 00:24:13.320
Carrying out international cooperation in aerospace

00:24:13.320 --> 00:24:14.960
is also an important strategy of ours.

00:24:14.960 --> 00:24:16.280
Someone has to do it.

00:24:17.920 --> 00:24:18.680
Mr. Jiang,

00:24:19.320 --> 00:24:20.320
with you leaving,

00:24:20.720 --> 00:24:22.600
I feel uneasy doing missions.

00:24:22.600 --> 00:24:23.680
Yeah, Mr. Jiang,

00:24:24.040 --> 00:24:25.240
please reconsider.

00:24:25.440 --> 00:24:26.960
All right, you don't need to persuade me.

00:24:26.960 --> 00:24:28.240
I've made my decision.

00:24:31.800 --> 00:24:33.660
It's not like I'm not coming back.

00:24:36.600 --> 00:24:37.480
Jiajia. Jia.

00:24:37.920 --> 00:24:38.600
Jia.

00:24:38.920 --> 00:24:39.560
She...

00:24:41.120 --> 00:24:41.720
Jia.

00:24:43.400 --> 00:24:44.080
Mengyao,

00:24:44.800 --> 00:24:45.880
I already heard.

00:24:46.720 --> 00:24:48.040
Thank you for being willing to do it for everyone,

00:24:48.040 --> 00:24:49.520
giving up the Haoyue mission

00:24:49.520 --> 00:24:51.920
and going abroad for the exchange program.

00:24:52.880 --> 00:24:54.280
However,

00:24:54.280 --> 00:24:56.120
I have already submitted the application form.

00:24:56.120 --> 00:24:57.120
I am going abroad.

00:24:59.240 --> 00:25:00.040
No, Jiajia.

00:25:00.040 --> 00:25:01.000
You can't go.

00:25:01.000 --> 00:25:02.800
What about the mission if you go?

00:25:03.720 --> 00:25:04.400
Jiajia,

00:25:04.720 --> 00:25:06.160
you must stay no matter what.

00:25:06.160 --> 00:25:07.320
The mission is more important, Jiajia.

00:25:07.320 --> 00:25:09.000
Right, you definitely can't go.

00:25:09.000 --> 00:25:10.000
Alright.

00:25:10.160 --> 00:25:10.760
Without me,

00:25:10.760 --> 00:25:12.440
the mission can't go on, right?

00:25:12.440 --> 00:25:13.000
Jiajia.

00:25:13.720 --> 00:25:14.400
Jia,

00:25:15.960 --> 00:25:17.120
I will miss you.

00:25:18.480 --> 00:25:20.360
Alright, I've made up my mind.

00:25:22.880 --> 00:25:25.000
I've been promoted now.

00:25:25.200 --> 00:25:26.400
I'm the team leader.

00:25:26.400 --> 00:25:27.520
You all have to listen to me.

00:25:27.520 --> 00:25:29.520
None of you are allowed to say anything else.

00:25:29.520 --> 00:25:30.160
Jiajia.

00:25:30.760 --> 00:25:31.400
Jia.

00:25:31.680 --> 00:25:32.520
Alright.

00:25:33.200 --> 00:25:34.480
The mission schedule is tight right now.

00:25:34.480 --> 00:25:35.740
Everyone, get to work.

00:25:36.960 --> 00:25:38.440
Hurry up and get to work.

00:25:39.400 --> 00:25:40.000
Go.

00:25:41.520 --> 00:25:42.780
Let's get back to work.

00:25:43.520 --> 00:25:44.920
I respect your decision.

00:25:56.000 --> 00:25:56.800
Jia.

00:25:58.480 --> 00:26:00.840
Have you told Wu Wei about this?

00:26:03.240 --> 00:26:04.200
Not yet.

00:26:04.960 --> 00:26:06.000
It's still early.

00:26:06.760 --> 00:26:08.120
I'll tell him

00:26:08.120 --> 00:26:09.450
when it's time to leave.

00:26:09.800 --> 00:26:10.600
Anyway,

00:26:11.240 --> 00:26:12.720
he's doing fine now.

00:26:12.960 --> 00:26:13.960
No, he's not.

00:26:14.880 --> 00:26:15.800
All right.

00:26:16.400 --> 00:26:17.330
Get back to work.

00:26:28.680 --> 00:26:29.400
Nan,

00:26:29.800 --> 00:26:30.680
did you know?

00:26:31.280 --> 00:26:32.480
Qi is leaving too.

00:26:34.160 --> 00:26:35.820
He and Xu Xu are going to Xi'an.

00:26:35.920 --> 00:26:37.760
They said they were seconded there

00:26:37.760 --> 00:26:39.420
to work on a mission together.

00:26:39.760 --> 00:26:41.290
Where did you get this news?

00:26:41.440 --> 00:26:42.770
Through the grapevine.

00:26:52.280 --> 00:26:53.810
Let's have a meal together.

00:27:23.520 --> 00:27:24.850
You're not mad, are you?

00:27:25.520 --> 00:27:26.520
What do you think?

00:27:30.680 --> 00:27:32.480
You know about me going to Xi'an.

00:27:36.000 --> 00:27:37.000
Actually, I originally...

00:27:37.000 --> 00:27:37.960
You never

00:27:38.960 --> 00:27:41.280
thought you should let me know.

00:27:43.240 --> 00:27:44.000
No.

00:27:44.520 --> 00:27:45.760
Such a big deal.

00:27:47.360 --> 00:27:48.420
What do you even...

00:27:51.120 --> 00:27:51.920
take me for...

00:27:53.440 --> 00:27:54.200
Forget it.

00:27:56.280 --> 00:27:57.400
Do you even

00:27:57.400 --> 00:27:58.720
consider me a friend?

00:28:03.480 --> 00:28:04.400
I was going to suggest

00:28:04.400 --> 00:28:05.840
we all go out for a meal.

00:28:07.520 --> 00:28:08.920
To make it more official.

00:28:17.080 --> 00:28:20.010
Jia is going abroad for an exchange program soon too.

00:28:22.720 --> 00:28:24.000
You are all leaving.

00:28:32.520 --> 00:28:33.520
It's all my fault.

00:28:34.560 --> 00:28:35.290
I apologize.

00:28:35.680 --> 00:28:37.480
I'll drink first out of respect.

00:28:38.040 --> 00:28:39.500
Consider this a farewell.

00:28:42.480 --> 00:28:43.880
What farewell?

00:28:45.200 --> 00:28:47.480
Are you leaving and never coming back?

00:28:53.360 --> 00:28:55.040
No matter how tight the schedule is,

00:28:55.040 --> 00:28:57.040
you'll still have holidays, right?

00:29:10.880 --> 00:29:11.740
Have a holiday.

00:29:13.320 --> 00:29:15.000
As long as I have a holiday,

00:29:15.680 --> 00:29:17.340
I will come back to see you all.

00:29:18.840 --> 00:29:20.080
I don't mean you all.

00:29:20.080 --> 00:29:21.840
I mean...

00:29:33.040 --> 00:29:33.720
Drink up.

00:29:38.160 --> 00:29:38.880
Since you are leaving,

00:29:38.880 --> 00:29:40.880
let's drink to our hearts' content.

00:29:42.520 --> 00:29:43.240
Cheers.

00:29:45.280 --> 00:29:47.340
However much you want to drink today,

00:29:47.480 --> 00:29:48.610
I'll drink with you.

00:30:10.800 --> 00:30:12.080
Drink a little slower.

00:30:19.520 --> 00:30:20.240
Ying Ziqi.

00:30:27.080 --> 00:30:28.080
Before you leave,

00:30:28.480 --> 00:30:30.840
do you have anything to say to me?

00:30:30.960 --> 00:30:31.560
Yes.

00:30:40.080 --> 00:30:41.000
Qu Ruonan.

00:30:56.960 --> 00:30:57.560
Ying Ziqi.

00:31:00.920 --> 00:31:01.840
Qu Ruonan.

00:31:03.440 --> 00:31:04.920
Here.

00:31:37.320 --> 00:31:38.920
Mr. Zhang, we're leaving.

00:31:38.920 --> 00:31:39.780
Okay, go ahead.

00:31:42.640 --> 00:31:43.480
After you go back,

00:31:43.480 --> 00:31:45.200
you must strictly follow the plan.

00:31:45.200 --> 00:31:46.360
Okay, Mr. Zhang.

00:31:46.560 --> 00:31:47.160
Go ahead.

00:31:51.600 --> 00:31:53.730
I hope you can take a look at this paper.

00:31:55.040 --> 00:31:56.600
How many times have I told you?

00:31:56.600 --> 00:31:57.730
I have my standards.

00:31:57.760 --> 00:32:00.420
If it works, it works. If it doesn't, it doesn't.

00:32:01.480 --> 00:32:03.040
This paper is about deep-space arrays

00:32:03.040 --> 00:32:06.570
and the analysis of spatial power combining characteristics.

00:32:08.200 --> 00:32:10.530
It will definitely help with the mission.

00:32:18.200 --> 00:32:18.920
Qi.

00:32:18.920 --> 00:32:20.520
Look at Nan.

00:32:20.520 --> 00:32:23.200
She even prepared toothbrushes and toothpaste.

00:32:23.200 --> 00:32:24.560
There's no need to bring so much.

00:32:24.560 --> 00:32:26.220
You can buy everything there.

00:32:26.680 --> 00:32:27.800
No way.

00:32:27.960 --> 00:32:29.320
Look at this coat.

00:32:29.320 --> 00:32:30.560
I prepared an extra one for you.

00:32:30.560 --> 00:32:31.920
And this emergency kit.

00:32:31.920 --> 00:32:33.200
And these bed sheets.

00:32:33.200 --> 00:32:34.960
I prepared an extra set of each for you.

00:32:34.960 --> 00:32:36.320
It's called being prepared.

00:32:36.320 --> 00:32:37.880
There's no need to bring so much.

00:32:37.880 --> 00:32:39.800
Just listen to whatever Nan says.

00:32:40.760 --> 00:32:41.480
By the way, Wei.

00:32:41.480 --> 00:32:42.640
Did you know

00:32:42.640 --> 00:32:44.040
that Jia is also leaving?

00:32:45.120 --> 00:32:46.080
Where is she going?

00:32:46.080 --> 00:32:47.200
She's going abroad for an exchange.

00:32:47.200 --> 00:32:49.400
She already signed up. Didn't you know?

00:32:50.360 --> 00:32:51.420
She didn't tell me.

00:33:00.200 --> 00:33:00.880
Coming.

00:33:08.440 --> 00:33:09.200
Mr. Zhang.

00:33:15.880 --> 00:33:17.140
I have read your paper.

00:33:17.440 --> 00:33:18.500
I came to inform you

00:33:18.920 --> 00:33:20.720
that the center has approved it.

00:33:21.000 --> 00:33:22.130
We depart tomorrow.

00:33:26.480 --> 00:33:28.740
You should pack your things quickly too.

00:33:30.880 --> 00:33:32.200
Are you going or not?

00:33:32.640 --> 00:33:34.040
I'm going.

00:33:34.600 --> 00:33:35.480
Tomorrow morning at 8 a.m.,

00:33:35.480 --> 00:33:37.120
meet at the entrance of the Aerospace City.

00:33:37.120 --> 00:33:37.960
Don't be late.

00:33:43.000 --> 00:33:43.800
Congratulations.

00:33:43.800 --> 00:33:45.480
Good news. Come.

00:33:47.680 --> 00:33:49.080
You are going to Kashgar.

00:33:49.320 --> 00:33:49.880
Congratulations.

00:33:49.880 --> 00:33:51.240
Work hard. Do your best.

00:33:51.560 --> 00:33:53.360
Sister Jia, you are leaving too.

00:33:53.360 --> 00:33:54.840
Come see me off tomorrow.

00:33:55.080 --> 00:33:56.480
I have something for you.

00:33:58.080 --> 00:33:59.740
Looks like I'm leaving first.

00:33:59.880 --> 00:34:01.960
Go, go, go. Everyone's leaving.

00:34:02.440 --> 00:34:04.840
Our Muxing Team is officially disbanded.

00:34:04.840 --> 00:34:06.370
What do you mean disbanded?

00:34:06.560 --> 00:34:08.800
We're just starting our own instances,

00:34:08.800 --> 00:34:10.800
fighting monsters and leveling up.

00:34:18.159 --> 00:34:19.219
Where is Ying Ziqi?

00:34:19.360 --> 00:34:21.679
He went to report to Xu Xu early this morning.

00:34:21.679 --> 00:34:23.480
What is there to report so early?

00:34:25.960 --> 00:34:26.480
Wei,

00:34:26.480 --> 00:34:27.679
we'll drop you off here.

00:34:27.679 --> 00:34:28.400
Thanks.

00:34:28.400 --> 00:34:29.080
Take care.

00:34:29.239 --> 00:34:29.679
See you.

00:34:29.679 --> 00:34:30.639
Bye.

00:34:32.760 --> 00:34:34.090
Let's wait a bit longer.

00:34:39.320 --> 00:34:39.960
Wu Wei.

00:34:44.040 --> 00:34:45.100
[China Aerospace]

00:34:48.639 --> 00:34:49.500
This is for you.

00:34:50.679 --> 00:34:51.520
What is this?

00:34:52.120 --> 00:34:53.179
These are my notes.

00:34:53.199 --> 00:34:54.159
Since I joined the flight control center,

00:34:54.159 --> 00:34:55.960
all my study materials are here.

00:34:56.280 --> 00:34:57.800
I think they should be helpful to you.

00:34:57.800 --> 00:34:59.860
You can take a look when you have time.

00:35:00.560 --> 00:35:01.160
Thank you.

00:35:01.640 --> 00:35:03.360
I have a gift for you too.

00:35:08.040 --> 00:35:10.240
Sister Jia, I'm leaving today.

00:35:10.240 --> 00:35:11.480
There are some things

00:35:11.480 --> 00:35:12.440
that if I don't say today,

00:35:12.440 --> 00:35:14.370
I'm afraid I won't have the chance.

00:35:16.160 --> 00:35:17.360
So,

00:35:17.360 --> 00:35:18.440
I want to tell you.

00:35:18.920 --> 00:35:20.780
I don't want to leave any regrets.

00:35:22.080 --> 00:35:23.440
Listen to you.

00:35:23.440 --> 00:35:25.040
It's not like we're parting forever.

00:35:25.040 --> 00:35:25.760
Besides,

00:35:25.960 --> 00:35:27.920
you're too old to be homesick.

00:35:29.640 --> 00:35:31.680
I'll miss home, and I'll also miss

00:35:43.680 --> 00:35:44.240
you, Jia.

00:35:45.040 --> 00:35:45.760
Actually.

00:35:50.480 --> 00:35:52.880
In my heart, you've long been more than just

00:35:53.120 --> 00:35:54.960
a senior, a teacher,

00:35:56.000 --> 00:35:56.660
or a leader.

00:36:01.720 --> 00:36:02.920
You are the one I like.

00:36:06.680 --> 00:36:08.200
I didn't realize it before.

00:36:08.200 --> 00:36:09.800
But now I'm absolutely sure.

00:36:09.800 --> 00:36:11.400
It's a man's love for a woman.

00:36:12.800 --> 00:36:15.360
I know it's not the best time to say this today.

00:36:16.360 --> 00:36:18.440
But in my flight path,

00:36:19.000 --> 00:36:20.040
you have long been

00:36:20.440 --> 00:36:22.170
the most important parameter.

00:36:25.640 --> 00:36:27.280
Wu Wei, I...

00:36:31.520 --> 00:36:33.380
Thank you for telling me all this.

00:36:33.640 --> 00:36:34.920
But between us...

00:36:34.920 --> 00:36:35.640
I understand, Jia.

00:36:35.640 --> 00:36:37.680
I know I'm not

00:36:37.680 --> 00:36:39.000
excellent or good enough yet.

00:36:39.000 --> 00:36:41.480
I'm not worthy of you, but don't worry.

00:36:41.480 --> 00:36:43.080
I will definitely work hard.

00:36:44.080 --> 00:36:44.920
No, no.

00:36:45.160 --> 00:36:46.320
This has nothing to do with being excellent

00:36:46.320 --> 00:36:47.960
or being worthy.

00:36:48.680 --> 00:36:50.200
We are of different ages,

00:36:50.360 --> 00:36:51.800
have different experiences,

00:36:51.800 --> 00:36:53.800
and are in different stages of life.

00:36:54.400 --> 00:36:55.360
Maybe...

00:36:56.080 --> 00:36:57.800
maybe I overthink things

00:36:57.920 --> 00:36:59.320
and consider too much.

00:36:59.800 --> 00:37:01.440
So I think we...

00:37:03.360 --> 00:37:05.320
I understand. I understand everything, Jia.

00:37:05.320 --> 00:37:06.120
I understand.

00:37:07.400 --> 00:37:08.000
No matter what,

00:37:08.000 --> 00:37:09.840
I hope you can accept this gift.

00:37:09.840 --> 00:37:10.760
Just treat it

00:37:14.320 --> 00:37:17.580
as a return gift from a younger brother to his older sister.

00:37:29.040 --> 00:37:29.770
I'm leaving.

00:37:30.320 --> 00:37:31.520
Good luck in Kashgar.

00:37:42.160 --> 00:37:42.890
I'm leaving.

00:37:44.240 --> 00:37:45.480
I'm heading out, Brother Bao, Sister Nan.

00:37:45.480 --> 00:37:46.880
Let's wait a little longer.

00:37:46.880 --> 00:37:47.800
I'm not waiting anymore.

00:37:47.800 --> 00:37:49.240
It's not like we won't see each other again.

00:37:49.240 --> 00:37:50.640
Give him a message for me.

00:37:50.880 --> 00:37:52.760
If he can't make it in Xi'an anymore,

00:37:52.760 --> 00:37:54.890
tell him to come to Kashgar and join me.

00:37:56.040 --> 00:37:56.770
Brother Wei.

00:37:57.840 --> 00:37:58.600
I'll miss you.

00:37:58.600 --> 00:38:00.160
Don't be so sentimental.

00:38:00.560 --> 00:38:01.360
My comrades.

00:38:01.680 --> 00:38:04.640
I'm heading far away without asking about what the future holds.

00:38:04.640 --> 00:38:05.500
See you around.

00:38:07.160 --> 00:38:09.440
Wait for me, Master Wu,

00:38:09.440 --> 00:38:10.640
to return in triumph.

00:38:11.480 --> 00:38:12.240
Take care.

00:38:12.400 --> 00:38:13.200
Brother Wei.

00:38:13.200 --> 00:38:14.000
Have a safe trip.

00:38:14.000 --> 00:38:15.440
I'll leave the rest to you.

00:38:15.440 --> 00:38:16.100
Okay, okay.

00:38:20.000 --> 00:38:20.800
Mr. Zhang.

00:38:21.520 --> 00:38:22.040
Okay.

00:38:23.000 --> 00:38:24.520
Goodbye.

00:38:24.760 --> 00:38:25.620
Bye, Mr. Zhang.

00:38:26.360 --> 00:38:26.920
Let's go.

00:38:26.920 --> 00:38:27.400
Good luck.

00:38:27.400 --> 00:38:27.760
Go.

00:39:04.120 --> 00:39:06.720
Man, you ride pretty wild.

00:39:10.640 --> 00:39:12.080
Don't break my BMW.

00:39:16.160 --> 00:39:17.690
Good luck with the mission.

00:39:17.920 --> 00:39:19.520
I'll wait for your good news.

00:39:20.600 --> 00:39:21.400
You too.

00:39:21.800 --> 00:39:22.930
When you go to Xi'an,

00:39:23.680 --> 00:39:24.520
stay strong.

00:39:26.920 --> 00:39:27.600
Sure.

00:39:29.520 --> 00:39:30.160
Go back.

00:39:35.600 --> 00:39:36.530
Have a safe trip.

00:39:41.600 --> 00:39:42.280
Baoma.

00:40:21.520 --> 00:40:23.780
The day I interviewed at Flight Control,

00:40:24.200 --> 00:40:25.880
I thought I was done for

00:40:26.680 --> 00:40:29.140
and could never pursue my space dream again.

00:40:35.960 --> 00:40:38.480
You were the one who gave me hope.

00:40:42.400 --> 00:40:44.130
Thank you for not giving up on me

00:40:44.440 --> 00:40:45.770
and teaching me so much.

00:40:50.680 --> 00:40:52.160
What you told me,

00:40:52.160 --> 00:40:53.880
I took it to heart.

00:40:54.760 --> 00:40:56.290
Just watch my performance.

00:41:04.040 --> 00:41:04.680
Also,

00:41:05.200 --> 00:41:06.730
you have to listen to me too.

00:41:07.000 --> 00:41:09.060
Please take good care of your health.

00:41:10.920 --> 00:41:12.720
You must listen to Mr. Gu

00:41:12.720 --> 00:41:14.000
and Director Cao.

00:41:14.200 --> 00:41:14.680
Okay.

00:41:26.600 --> 00:41:27.680
Mr. Gu,

00:41:28.160 --> 00:41:30.400
thank you for scolding me so harshly

00:41:31.600 --> 00:41:33.600
and taming this wild monkey.

00:41:34.480 --> 00:41:35.320
I know

00:41:35.320 --> 00:41:36.920
you did it for my own good.

00:41:37.600 --> 00:41:39.330
I will definitely remember it.

00:41:43.720 --> 00:41:44.520
Actually,

00:41:45.920 --> 00:41:47.560
you are a very gentle person.

00:41:48.120 --> 00:41:50.160
I hope you can smile more from now on.

00:41:59.560 --> 00:42:00.200
And,

00:42:00.560 --> 00:42:01.760
Mr. Qin promised that

00:42:01.760 --> 00:42:03.320
even if he has to use a cane,

00:42:03.320 --> 00:42:04.980
he'll watch me go on a mission.

00:42:06.120 --> 00:42:07.850
To make this promise come true,

00:42:07.880 --> 00:42:09.000
I'll leave Mr. Qin

00:42:09.000 --> 00:42:10.200
in your good hands.

00:42:26.840 --> 00:42:27.800
Flight control

00:42:27.800 --> 00:42:29.160
is my second home.

00:42:29.240 --> 00:42:30.480
You are all my family.

00:42:31.720 --> 00:42:32.320
Keep it up.

00:42:32.320 --> 00:42:33.040
Keep it up.

